com.google.api.ads.dfp.lib.client

Class DfpSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.ads.dfp.lib.client.DfpSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientLoginCompatible, OAuth2Compatible, AdsSession

    public class DfpSession
extends Object
implements AdsSession, OAuth2Compatible, ClientLoginCompatible
    A DfpSession represents a single session of DFP use.

    Implementation is not thread-safe.

    Author:
    Adam Rogal
